global_flags.description: Write output in LLVM intermediate language (instead of bitcode).
this  is a debug build, this option will enable debug print outs from passes which use the LLVM_DEBUG() macro.  See the LLVM Programmer's Manual, section #DEBUG for more information.

Enable binary output on terminals.  Normally, opt will refuse to write raw bitcode output if the output  stream  is  a  terminal. With  this  option, opt will write raw bitcode regardless of the output device.
Print a summary of command line options.
